{"tid":1688716,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"罷叫支那雞， 罷屌支那閪","createTime":"2019-11-02T14:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T14:14:41.000Z","uid":304769,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"812ae8cad4ae9339ffb26fb7da1e9fe45641a582","tid":1688716,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:08:20.000Z","msg":"事源我尋日去Swire食完東南亞餐,響KK Leung度等𨋢上返main library ，居然畀我聽到兩個疑似year 1 freshman賽后包搞膠佢地去上環揾北姑破處既經歷，我當場嬲到屌柒佢兩個，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個時勢仲幫襯北姑？唔L係吖？仲比千幾蚊外匯支那人賺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />梗係支持陀地，最好係黃絲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n但係我屌完佢兩個就發現一個問題，就係我地<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃藍地圖太集中餐飲，未有涵蓋其他範疇</span></span></strong>，例如性工作者。這樣的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黃藍地圖明顯不完美，要改善</span></strong>。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我們要將黃藍地圖同米豬連推廣到性工作者</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等手足可以去真正大大力懲罰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋奶下黃絲閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚮未有之前，我唯有教佢地上叫雞網用screener篩走支那閪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">贊成請正評並推</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">另外，對於經濟戰，我有以下看法：</span><br />\n黃絲經濟圈不只是流於形式的吃飯要幫襯黃店，而是要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建立黃絲互助互愛的精神，是一個long-term commitment</span></span></strong>。<br />\n而一直無人提及，我想提出的是我們要讓<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃絲雇主主動提供就業機會給在這場運動中付出的人，無論是因為運動而學業中斷，被炒，坐監還是受傷。我們不是要同情他們，而是要懷著感恩的心感激他們對社會的付出。我希望各位黃絲的老闆以及HR可以明白呢點。</span></span></strong><br />\n另外一方面，我們也要全面擴大黃絲經濟圈。食飯，手機這種日常消費固然是最重要的。但是也<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不要忽略其他非恆常性開支例如買書</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1629142/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1629142/page/1</a><br />\n［香港本土書店 List］罷買三中商，然後呢？<br />\n也要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">把黃絲經濟圈的內容加上英文推廣給外國訪港旅客以及本地非華裔人口</span></span></strong><br />\n以及也要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">把stand with Hong Kong, Boycott China推廣到全球，大家一齊罷買中國產品</span></span></strong>。而這一點<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">先從自己做起，買野記得睇標籤，見到Made in China/Product of China就放翻上架</span></span></strong>。只要大家齊心，好快Made in China就會滯銷然後唔再入貨。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家幫手推，尤其請人果點好重要，幫我推到黃絲老闆睇到</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"451d31f3aafc3b1905806bc18b986f6d16bc30a1","tid":1688716,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"有啲惡搞,太揚一定搞到啲陀地一樓一"},{"pid":"ad05b91761419f6720f494f527dad93630a38bf5","tid":1688716,"uid":301989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:13:11.000Z","msg":"on9精蟲上腦"},{"pid":"e6cea2ed25461845238a5c26950ee8d41d62b8a5","tid":1688716,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"451d31f3aafc3b1905806bc18b986f6d16bc30a1","tid":1688716,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"有啲惡搞,太揚一定搞到啲陀地一樓一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:13:58.000Z","msg":"認證黃絲通訊軟件帳戶，先從網上接客既（例如援交妹）落手。一樓一遲d先，我都怕佢睇睇會比黑精警搞"},{"pid":"2dc628062ca4fc18e76035f1ed1e0ab6474f1c91","tid":1688716,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"451d31f3aafc3b1905806bc18b986f6d16bc30a1","tid":1688716,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"有啲惡搞,太揚一定搞到啲陀地一樓一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:14:41.000Z","msg":"認證黃絲通訊軟件帳戶，先從網上接客既（例如援交妹）落手。一樓一遲d先，我都怕佢地會比黑警搞"}]}